eilkunst and homeopathic consultation services.","location":"Pahoa","rating":5,"lat":19.503306,"lng":-154.903636,"tier":"free","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"8f5aa127-70e8-45bd-a5ff-518c8ee6b243","name":"Hawaiian Ethos","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/5956fd9ae110eba6434be862/t/5f667cb8179c39639dfb52c7/1600552123715/Website_redesign-02.jpg?format=1500w","type":"practitioner","modality":"Herbalism","modalities":["Herbalism"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Sustainable, local, medical cannabis dispensary located on the Big Island of Hawaii.","location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.692191,"lng":-156.017358,"tier":"free","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"ca914b11-b525-4e7b-9021-bd67ef9d808d","name":"Unlock Your Natural Vitality","image":"http://healingnoni.com/cdn/shop/files/Healingnoni.com_website_preview.jpg?v=1765999589","type":"practitioner","modality":"Herbalism","modalities":["Herbalism"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Discover Healing Noni, your source for premium noni juice and natural wellness solutions. Learn how noni supports immunity, digestion, energy, and overall health through time tested traditions and modern quality standards. Shop, explore benefits, and start your wellness journey today.","location":"Pāhoa","rating":5,"lat":19.44475,"lng":-154.917458,"tier":"free","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"6c13c86d-414c-4a89-98d7-540566c6e026","name":"Lauran Chapple","businessName":"Oceanic Wellness","image":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/84770f_6efb5a8a5b454f79b93f4e5cfd701fccf000.jpg/v1/fill/w_288,h_105,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/84770f_6efb5a8a5b454f79b93f4e5cfd701fccf000.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Acupuncture, Herbalism","modalities":["Acupuncture","Herbalism"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Acupuncture is the placement of tiny needles along meridians or trigger points to stimulate the body's own natural healing abilities. Acupuncture treatments may also include moxibustion, cupping, massage, essential oils, e-stim, magnets ear seeds or tacks. Acupuncture can be helpful for relieving pain, reducing stress and providing relief from a wide variety of symptoms.","location":"Waimea","rating":5,"lat":19.932919,"lng":-155.792483,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"91fbd113-9a2f-4556-92f3-8a09ba0f7e5f","name":"Mei-jen Stokesbary","image":"","type":"practitioner","modality":"Acupuncture, Herbalism","modalities":["Acupuncture","Herbalism"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"","location":"Waimea","rating":5,"lat":0,"lng":0,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T20:18:10.862484+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"936ec842-a311-460b-8302-6ef8e0ba8e47","name":"Mei-jen Sun Stokesbary, L.Ac.","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/practitioners/1773111615274-dxf6c2rx2x.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Acupuncture, TCM (Traditional Chinese Medicine), Herbalism","modalities":["Acupuncture","TCM (Traditional Chinese Medicine)","Herbalism"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Mei-jen Sun Stokesbary, L.Ac. is a licensed acupuncturist on the Big Island of Hawaii. She provides Oriental Medicine consultations, structural alignment exams and treatments of musculoskeletal disharmonies. She provides diet & nutritional counseling to help balance your system. She comes from a long line of doctors, surgeons, and healers.","location":"Waimea","rating":5,"lat":20.082276,"lng":-155.83368,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"4765f902-063c-4f59-97f4-1380272e8f34","name":"Sacred Nectar Medicinals","image":"https://i0.wp.com/sacrednectarmedicinals.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cleanse-3pack.png?fit=300%2C229&ssl=1","type":"practitioner","modality":"Herbalism","modalities":["Herbalism"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Hear from our clients, worldwide, who have experienced deep nourishment, clearing and transformation using Sacred Nectar Medicinals.","location":"Pāhoa","rating":5,"lat":19.361504,"lng":-154.978205,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false}],"centers":[{"id":"5978c7a1-c13e-4b5c-9d7f-4a34276f2b87","name":"Aloha Regenerative Therapy of Hawaii","image":"https://primary.jwwb.nl/public/g/h/b/temp-hwkckrnzwdkzaznjxhiu/acupuncture-for-athletes-7-high-dyw7cy.webp?enable-io=true&enable=upscale&fit=bounds&width=1200","modality":"Psychotherapy, Acupuncture, Herbalism, Longevity","modalities":["Psychotherapy","Acupuncture","Herbalism","Longevity"],"location":"Pahoa","rating":5,"lat":19.47256,"lng":-154.915852,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Accupuncture, Alternative medicine, holistic medicine, needless stem cell therapy, reflexology, lymphatic drainage, cupping and much more!","centerType":"clinic","centerTypeLabel":"Clinic","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"9013c4e1-0fa8-4c5e-80d4-62f41c0037a9","name":"Mana Wellness Massage Therapy & Holistic Health","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/729961b9d1321704102c925635d327f6.jpg","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Counseling, Herbalism, Lomilomi / Hawaiian Healing, Massage, Naturopathic, Network Chiropractic, Osteopathic","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Counseling","Herbalism","Lomilomi / Hawaiian Healing","Massage","Naturopathic","Network Chiropractic","Osteopathic"],"location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.724544,"lng":-155.08623,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Nestled in downtown Hilo, Hawaii on the Big Island, Mana Wellness Massage Therapy & Holistic Health provides professional massage therapy at our convienient location at 224 Kamehameha Ave Ste 206 Hilo, HI 96720. Wehope you give yourself the opprotunity for some massage & relaxation at our small Spa.","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"497e70a0-17a0-4ec7-acaf-998a501a79aa","name":"Starseed Ranch","image":"https://starseedranch.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/SS_tropicalbouquet6.png","modality":"Herbalism","modalities":["Herbalism"],"location":"Kapaau","rating":5,"lat":20.216489,"lng":-155.747871,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"E Komo Mai . Welcome to the pristine northern coast of Hawai’i island. The Kohala Mountains are sacred verdant lands filled with the abundance of the natural world – valleys, streams, mountains, forests and farms. Come enjoy our peaceful and healing accommodations. Visit tropical permaculture food forests and taste a diversity of fresh fruits, vegetables, roots, medicines and spices. Experience an ancient agricultural setting filled with the rich history of native Hawai’ian culture. A visit to Starseed Ranch is an adventure sure to inspire.","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true}],"totalPractitioners":9,"totalCenters":3,"citiesServed":["Hilo","Kailua-Kona","Kapaau","Pahoa","Pāhoa","Waimea"]}]
